channel.title: My Mass Effect inspired song
channel.description:
I'm trying to make music that would fit in video games because I would like to contribute my music to the modding community. Enjoy and let me know what you think. If you could see this being used in the actual game or a mod, please say so. :3 Its only a minute long at the moment. I plan to add more to it, but its coming slowly. [url]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zju5970QZsk[/url]
Here is a link to the download of the full mp3: [url='https://rapidshare.com/files/390786610/5-18-2010.mp3']Clicky[/url]
